## What is Cazuela?

Cazuela is a lightweight framework written in PHP that allows you to export data to common formats such as JSON/XML/YAML. PDO used as data layer.

It can be used to interconnect systems, such as middleware platform, such as API layer or whatever you can think of!

## Supported Databases

For now only MySQL and PostgreSQL

## How to use?

See the example in the app /services/Test.php (Wiki is still under construction).

Then in your favorite browser:

http://domain/Test/getTest.(xml/json/yml)

